  "remarks": "Yemeni national identification number 973406, issued on 3 Jul. 1996. Yemeni passport number 00344994, issued on 3 Jul. 1999 in Sanaa.  Mother's name: Fatima Muthanna Yahya. Photo available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice.  Leader of Al-Qaida in the Arabian Peninsula (QDe. 129) since Jun. 2015, pleaded loyalty to Aiman al-Zawahiri (QDi.006). As of February 2020, reportedly killed in a counterterrorism operation in Yemen. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed 11 May 2010 (amended  on 15 Apr. 2014, 24 Jun. 2016, 24 Nov. 2020, 11 Mar. 2025)",
